  it to the last (management) form;
  Since management with the name filed should be browsed all the time,
  conditional dictionary is not needed anymore and 'drop_wm_form',
  which controls the form appearance is no longer necessary.
  In this commit conditional dict and drop_wm_form are dropped.
  But 'stay_at_the_catalog' checkbox is appeared in case application
  creation form was called directly from the catalog and it's not
  a dependancy application (in case applciation was callwd via '+'
  this checkbox is not needed);

* Insert 'name' to the object modal header;

* Get name field from object modal header or directly from object modal;

* Add name function to the YAQL context;

* Optimize application creation wizard;

* Update tests.

